strings: <voice_0x01000EF4><se_def>the prince carlos: <leader> Let's see what you make!
<voice_0x01000EF5><se_def>the prince carlos: So... gecko, eh? According to the seller, Argonia lizard-like lizards.
<voice_0x01000EF6><se_def>the prince carlos: A sleeping lizard woke up to a slight smell! I think that's enough for the show!
